  "frontCover": "Front cover of a greeting card, watercolor style, 9:16 ratio. Features a split composition with two stylized cartoon characters. On the left, a character with dark hair pulled back, wearing glasses, a grey sweater, and dark pants, holds a paintbrush and looks distressed, with a single drop of grey paint falling from the brush. Their expression is a frown. On the right, a joyful character with dark hair, splattered with vibrant rainbow colors on their face, shirt, and pants, holds multiple paintbrushes with colorful bristles. This character is smiling broadly, with paint splatters around them. The background on the right is a dynamic, abstract watercolor wash of bright blues, greens, yellows, oranges, and reds. The background on the left is a muted, creamy beige with a subtle paper texture. The text \"Happy Birthday Geihs\" is written in a flowing, elegant brown handwritten cursive script, positioned centrally and safely away from the edges. The overall mood is humorous, depicting a contrast between artistic struggle and artistic triumph.",
